metadata.name: Crypto Chameleons Club #1
metadata.description: Our 7000 Crypto Chameleons Club NFTs are your ticket to a community and project that is focused on growing the wealth of CCC holders through large Ethereum giveaways and a NFT Fund that is run by the holders! By holding a Crypto Chameleon NFT, you are able to receive payouts of the fund as well as play a role in what projects the fund holds! This is just the beginning.
